      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルでも姉でもない、高校生としての沙季……か）\n（また一つ、新たな一面を見ることが出来たな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Not as an idol or a big sister‚ but as a high school student… huh.）\n（I've witnessed another new side of her.）",
