      "text": "それが……友達が「あそこのスーツの人は誰？」\n「凄く優しそうだね」なんて言い始めまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… my friends started saying‚ \"Who's that person in the suit\nover there? Seems very kind.\"",
