      "text": "そのうち「沙季とどういう関係？」なんて、まるで教室\nで恋愛の話をする時みたいにはしゃいでしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then they got all excited‚ saying‚ \"What's the relationship between you and that person?\"\nIt was like talking about love in the classroom…",
        "id": ""
